Class Car

  • java.lang.Object
    • Car
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Saab95, Volvo240
    public abstract class Car
extends java.lang.Object
    A class for Car. Contains necessary methods to make a car move (speed up, slow down, turn). Assumes "forward" is up.
    Author:
    pepegas
